<HEADLINE> Ge Fei, Gu Jun Takes Women's Doubles </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
GLASGOW, Scotland, June 1 (Xinhua) -- China's Ge Fei and Gu Jun
beat fellow partners Qin Yiyuan and Tang Yongshu 15-1, 15-8 in the
final to take the women's doubles title at the World Badminton
Championships here on Sunday. 
</P>
