<P>
SINGAPORE, June 2 (Xinhua) -- Share prices continued to slip
lower on the Singapore market as the benchmark Straits Times
Industrials Index fell by 4.58 points to close at 2,060.9 points
today.
</P>
<P>
The total market volume was still thin at 108.88 million units,
