<HEADLINE> Shanghai Stock Index up </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, June 2 (Xinhua) -- The Composite Stock Index on the
Shanghai Stock Exchange finished at 1,336.23, up 51.10 points from
the previous closing, according to the China Finance Trust and
Investment Corporation.
</P>
<P>
