<HEADLINE> Human Resources Network Established In North China </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
TIANJIN, June 2 (Xinhua) -- A network to promote cooperation on
human resources exchanges in provinces and cities around the Bohai
Sea has been set up in north China's port city of Tianjin.
</P>
<P>
