<BODY>
<HEADLINE> Domestic Name-Brand Products Are Mainstay of Chinese Market </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, June 2 (Xinhua) -- A survey headed by the State
Statistics Bureau has revealed that 33 domestic name-brand
products among the 44 sampled have a marketshare of more than 70
percent, and such products as refrigerators and washing machines
have a market share of more than 90 percent.
</P>
<P>
Domestic name-brand products for daily use such as
water-heating machines, instant noodles, alcohol, and clothing
have a solid foundation, with production capabilities and product
quality reaching high levels.
</P>
<P>
Competition is fierce in the market of color TVs, micro-wave
ovens, and motor-cycles, but domestic name-brand products have
gained a firm foothold.
</P>
<P>
In 1996, 72 percent of the air-conditioning market was made up
of domestic name-brand products. The ratio is expected to rise to
79 percent in the next three years.
</P>
<P>
Foreign-brand products, however, still hold the lead in some
areas. For example, 68 percent of the consumers surveyed would
like to buy foreign-brand component stereo equipment. 
</P>
</TEXT>
</BODY>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> XIE19970602.0232 </DOCNO>
<DATE_TIME> 1997-06-02 </DATE_TIME>
<BODY>
<HEADLINE> Nanjing Offers Insurance for Job Injury, Birth </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
NANJING, June 2 (Xinhua) -- The capital city of east China's
Jiangsu province is offering insurance coverage for job injuries,
and pregnancy and birth, in another step taken by the city to
build an all-inclusive social security plan.
</P>
<P>
Nanjing currently provides an old-age pension and unemployment
insurance, which aid 95 percent and 90 percent of its residents
respectively.
</P>
<P>
Now with city requires all the businesses within the city's
jurisdiction to participate in the new job injury, and pregnancy
and birth insurance programs.
</P>
<P>
The job injury insurance covers injuries and deaths which occur
during rescue operation, sudden deaths from diseases caused by work
stress, and injuries and deaths from traffic accidents between the
victim's home and workplace.
</P>
<P>
The pregnancy and birth insurance covers pays for women during
their maternity leave, and medical examinations, operations,
hospitalization, and other costs during pregnancy and birth.
</P>
<P>
As a measure to check the incidence of job injuries, the
businesses are required to pay into the mutual assistance fund for
job injuries at rates in accordance with the degrees of risks
involved in their work.  
</P>
</TEXT>
</BODY>
</DOC>
